                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i5">
                            <locus from="126ra" to="133va"/>
                            <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4872MaqdemaWangel">Introduction to the Gospels</title>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ <t:gap xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" reason="ellipsis"/> ንቅድም፡ በረድኤተ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ሎቱ፡ ስብሐት፡ 
                                <t:supplied xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" reason="omitted" resp="PRS8999Strelcyn">ይትባረክ፡ ስሙ፡</t:supplied> ወይትለዓል፡ ዝክሩ፡ ወፍጽምናሁ፡ ዘእምኔሁ፡ ሢመተ፡ ኵሉ፡ 
                                ኃይል፡ ወቦቱ፡ ተፍጻሜተ፡ ኵሉ፡ ስእለት፤ ወኀቤሁ፡ ምብጻሐ፡ ኵሉ፡ አስተብቍዖት፡ በጽሒፈ፡ መቅድመ፡ ፬፡ ወንጌላት፡ 
                                <t:supplied xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" reason="undefined" resp="PRS8999Strelcyn">ስቡሓት፡ ወ፡</t:supplied>ቅዱሳት። ወ፲አቅማራት፡ በሰላመ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ አሜን። </incipit>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i6">
                            <locus from="134ra" to="148ra"/>
                            <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT6468Astebeqweot">ʾAstabǝqʷǝʿot ʾǝnta za-Sǝmʿon ʿAmdāwi</title>
                            <t:note xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Prayers of St Simeon Stylites for the days of the week, beginning with Monday.</t:note>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ <t:gap xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" reason="ellipsis"/> ንወጥን፡ በረድኤተ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ክቡር፡ ወልዑል፡ ወበሥነ፡ ስርሐቱ፡ በጽሒፈ፡ ጸሎት፡ 
                                ወአስተብቍዖት፡ እንተ፡ ዘስምዖን፡ ዓምዳዊ። ቀዳሚሃ፡ ዘእግዝእትነ፡ ማርያም፡ ወድንግልት፡ በክልኤ።</incipit>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i7">
                            <locus from="148ra" to="148vb"/>
                            <title>Unidentified Prayer ascribed to St Simeon Stylites</title>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">ካልእ፡ ጸሎቱ፡ ዘቅዱስ፡ አባ፡ ስምዖን፡ በዓለ፡ አምድ፡ ሀበኒ፡ ኦእግዚአብሔር፡ ጸሎተ፡ ዘእንበለ፡ ነጎጋው።</incipit>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i8">
                            <locus from="148vb" to="149va"/>
                            <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4239Prayer">Prayer of Ephrem for the twilight</title>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">ጸሎቱ፡ ዘቅዱስ፡ አባ፡ ኤፍሬም፡ <t:supplied xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" reason="omitted" resp="Strelcyn">ሶርያዊ፡</t:supplied> 
                                ኦእግዚእየ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶርስ፡ ተዘከርኩ፡ ይእተ፡ ሰዓተ፤ ወፈራህኩ። </incipit>
                        </msItem>     
