                        <additions>
                            <list>
                                <item xml:id="a1">
                                    <locus from="65ra" to="66ra"/>
                                    <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2940RepCh221">Malkǝʾ-hymn to Our Lady Mary</title>
                                    <desc type="GuestText"/>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez">ሰላም፡ ሰላም፡ ለዝክር፡ ስምኪ፡ በአምሐ፡ </q>
                                </item>
                                <item xml:id="a2">
                                    <locus target="#125v"/>
                                    <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4875Reliability">Introduction on the Reliability of the Gospels</title>
                                    <desc type="GuestText"/>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ <t:gap xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" reason="ellipsis"/> ስብሐት፡ ለእግዚአብሔር፡ መዓርገ፡ ወንጌላት፡ ወዝማሬ፡ ዘበአማን፡ በተአምራት፡ ግሁዳት፡ 
                                        እምኵሎሙ፡ ሐዋርያት፡ ወኵሎሙ፡ መንክራት፡ መዋዔ፡ ኵሉ፡ ልቡናት፡ ወወትከሥት፡ ቦቱ፡ ጽድቀ፡ ሃይማኖት፡ <t:gap xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" reason="ellipsis"/></q>
                                </item>
                                <item xml:id="a3">
                                    <locus target="#126r"/>
                                    <desc type="Unclear">An Amharic note of seven lines on the upper margin.</desc>
                                    <q xml:lang="am"/>
                                </item>
                                <item xml:id="a4">
                                    <locus target="#133va"/>
                                    <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3058RepCh338">ʾƎsaggǝd laki ʾǝsaggǝd laki ʾǝsaggǝd laki
          wa-ʾǝweddǝsaki</title>
                                    <desc type="GuestText"/>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez">እሰግድ፡ ለኪ፡ ወእዌድስኪ፡ ኦእግዝእትየ፡ ማርያም፡ በከመ፡ ወደስኪ፡ በድርሳኑ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ አፈ፡ ወርቅ፡ እንዘ፡ ይብል፡ ተፈስሒ፡ 
                                        ኦእግዝእትየ፡ <t:supplied xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" reason="omitted" resp="Strelcyn">ማርያም፡</t:supplied></q>
                                </item>
                                <item xml:id="e1">
                                    <locus target="#1 #1v #2r #3r #142r #149vb"/>
                                    <desc type="Unclear">Short notes, pen trials.</desc>
                                </item>
                                <item xml:id="e2">
                                    <locus target="#3r #6r #11v #12v #14r #14v #15r #126r"/>
                                    <desc type="Unclear">In the margins there are many notes written in a very small and fine script by at least three
                                        different hands, some in Amharic.</desc>
                                    <q xml:lang="am"/>
                                </item>
                                <item xml:id="e3">
